Package entity

Class Project

java.lang.Object
entity.Project
public class Project extends Object
The Project class represents a project with various attributes such as project name,neighborhood, unit types, sell prices and many more.

    • Project

      public Project(String name, String neighborhood, int numType1, int sellPrice1, int numType2, int sellPrice2, Date openDate, Date closeDate, String manager, int numOfficerSlots, String[] officers, String visibility)
      Constructs a Project with the specified details. Used when loading from csv.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the project.
      neighborhood - The neighborhood where the project is located.
      numType1 - The number of units for type 1 in the project.
      sellPrice1 - The selling price of a unit of type 1.
      numType2 - The number of units for type 2 in the project.
      sellPrice2 - The selling price of a unit of type 2.
      openDate - The opening date of the project.
      closeDate - The closing date of the project.
      manager - The name of the manager overseeing the project.
      numOfficerSlots - The number of officer slots available for the project.
      officers - The array of officers assigned to the project.
      visibility - The visibility status of the project (e.g., public, private).
